@Transactional(readOnly=true, rollbackFor=java.lang.Exception.class) @Service public class TemporaryStorageServiceImpl extends Object implements TemporaryStorageService
This class holds methods to perform CRUD operation on 'temporarystorage' table through its DAO layer.
